    "We provide the details and results in Appendix C.5.",
    "Table 3 shows the ASR-valid of agents with valid rates greater than 50%.",
    "We show the results of other agents in Appendix C.2 and the ASR-all in Appendix C.3.",
    "In addition to presenting the overall ASR for each setting, we also detail the ASRs for two attack categories.",
    "For data stealing attacks specifically, we provide a detailed breakdown of the success rates across two steps: data extraction and subsequent transmission."
